{"tid":318764,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[日本痴線佬ARuFa]因為想成為魔法少女、所以試著製造只屬於我的「使魔」","createTime":"2017-07-12T10:19:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-13T06:23:23.000Z","uid":75969,"like":186,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"01115df6725f8283dee3bf2f92e77ac3b141df01","tid":318764,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T10:19:52.000Z","msg":"大家好、我是<strong>ARuFa</strong>。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://nuwton.com/assets/uploads/2017/06/1498725923d1lut.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnuwton.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2F1498725923d1lut.jpg&h=86817e32&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然有點突然但是有一個問題想問。大家在<strong>小時候有過憧憬的職業</strong>嗎？<br />\n <br />\n我自己的話、有一段時期曾經想過<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">「要成為魔法少女」</span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://nuwton.com/assets/uploads/2017/06/14987259255b4s4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnuwton.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2F14987259255b4s4.png&h=ed3f796c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n用可愛的衣服包裹著身體、驅使魔法守護和平的<strong>魔法少女</strong>。<br />\n <br />\n電視播放<strong>「小魔女DoReMi」</strong>正好是在我上小學的時期、因此觸發了我對魔法少女的憧憬。<br />\n <br />\n雖然如此、能夠成為魔法少女的只有<strong>『被選中的少女』</strong>。歲月流逝、變成了離少女最遠的<strong>「成年男性」</strong>的我如今、放棄了魔法少女的夢想在公司裡工作<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://nuwton.com/assets/uploads/2017/06/1498730761unfmb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnuwton.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2F1498730761unfmb.jpg&h=29e88a3f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n但是、我並沒有放棄魔法少女的全部。<br />\n <br />\n<strong>對&hellip;&hellip;既然不能成為魔法少女的話&hellip;&hellip;那麼至少&hellip;&hellip;</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://nuwton.com/assets/uploads/2017/06/14987259288thz6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnuwton.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2F14987259288thz6.png&h=3f51c194&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">想要一隻&rdquo;使魔&rdquo;！</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n大家知道嗎？在魔法少女的旁邊、有相當高的機率會浮遊著被稱為<strong>「使魔」</strong>的小動物<br />\n<br />\n倒不如說、<span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>使魔的存在才是令魔法少女足以稱為魔法少女的理由</strong></span>。<br />\n<br />\n就是這樣、今次要製作魔法少女的伙伴使魔、希望令自己變得更接近魔法少女。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://nuwton.com/assets/uploads/2017/06/1498733183di43s.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnuwton.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2F1498733183di43s.png&h=fd664bde&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n(1.不清楚是什麼動物<br />\n2.眼睛很大<br />\n3.長著羽毛<br />\n4.有一些標記)<br />\n事不宜遲、製作使魔不可缺少的因素、由我至今看到<strong>「使魔的種種」</strong>之中裡選出一些。<br />\n <br />\n今次、要製作滿足以上<strong>4</strong>個條件的使魔。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://nuwton.com/assets/uploads/2017/06/1498725931dx6wp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnuwton.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2F1498725931dx6wp.jpg&h=d25d3d98&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n <br />\n首先買回來的是、要成為使魔『身體』的<strong>毛公仔</strong>。<br />\n<br />\n去了玩具反斗城、尋找最像使魔的毛公仔、結果就是這個像中了毒狀態的浣熊。<br />\n<br />\n雖然眼睛很大和毛色很活潑鮮艷是很好、但作為浣熊的感覺還是太強、所以為了滿足今次『不清楚是什麼動物』的條件、<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://nuwton.com/assets/uploads/2017/06/149872593373cqv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnuwton.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2F149872593373cqv.jpg&h=e6c5a385&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n稍為改造了一下這個小型犬用的頸圈、<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://nuwton.com/assets/uploads/2017/06/1498725935dxxxz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnuwton.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2F1498725935dxxxz.jpg&h=dceeb304&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>變得有點像老鼠的耳朵</strong>。只是耳朵改變了、就增強了不少不清楚是什麼動物的感覺。<br />\n<br />\n現在就已經變得相當可愛、但今次為了加強角色感&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://nuwton.com/assets/uploads/2017/06/1498725937eoimm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnuwton.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2F1498725937eoimm.jpg&h=f89f4eb2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n幫它戴上了<strong>王冠</strong>。<br />\n<br />\n在「使魔的種種」之中、也有<strong>「附著人間界的道具」</strong>的類型、這樣的話角色的Good accent就出來了。<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">(sorry,呢到唔係好明up乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://nuwton.com/assets/uploads/2017/06/14987259397b0oj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnuwton.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2F14987259397b0oj.jpg&h=789f478b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而且還有、挪用在橫濱中華街買的「諸葛孔明團扇」製造成<span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>羽毛</strong></span>&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://nuwton.com/assets/uploads/2017/06/1498787982d03ih.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnuwton.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2F1498787982d03ih.jpg&h=d4dd1012&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後、用細小的配件裝飾全身的話&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://nuwton.com/assets/uploads/2017/06/14987278731bl9k.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnuwton.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2F14987278731bl9k.jpg&h=e4c0ab79&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>只屬於我的「使魔」完成！</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n覺得如何？由「使魔的種種」組成、<strong>只屬於我的使魔誕生了</strong>。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://nuwton.com/assets/uploads/2017/06/1498788578avv7m.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnuwton.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2F1498788578avv7m.png&h=2229f8da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然羽毛有點噁心、但也跟可愛的外表成對比、感覺身為角色的個性也昇華了。<br />\n<br />\n順提一帶名字是<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">「太姆太姆」</span></strong>！好好相處吧！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://nuwton.com/assets/uploads/2017/06/14987259196wm7d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnuwton.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2F14987259196wm7d.jpg&h=4d1f5b64&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n從後面看是這樣。毛茸茸的尾巴。而且從後面看的話羽毛變得更加噁心。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://nuwton.com/assets/uploads/2017/06/1498725921crkve.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnuwton.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2F1498725921crkve.jpg&h=b6af4b11&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外只要用釣竿釣起來的話、就能讓它像使魔一樣在<strong>空中浮遊</strong>。<br />\n<br />\n&hellip;&hellip;來吧、既然已經完成了使魔、接下來就稍為偷窺一下「假如自己成為了魔法少女」的世界吧。<br />\n<br />\n好！ 要成為嚮往的魔法少女了哦！！"},{"pid":"b6354ff237cbd0569cf0084e2a37e5337bed9e87","tid":318764,"uid":75969,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T10:20:49.000Z","msg":"<strong>魔法少女☆ポプリン的日常</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://nuwton.com/assets/uploads/2017/06/14987894147ws0d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnuwton.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2F14987894147ws0d.jpg&h=a590d57a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n早上好！ 我是ARuFa。26歲的普通公司職員。<br />\n <br />\n雖然是個沒有任何可取之處的我、其實&hellip;&hellip;我有著不能對任何人說的<strong>&rdquo;秘密&rdquo;</strong>―――<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://nuwton.com/assets/uploads/2017/06/1498789397dsjtn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnuwton.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2F1498789397dsjtn.jpg&h=823bb707&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://nuwton.com/assets/uploads/2017/06/149878989252y7g.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnuwton.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2F149878989252y7g.png&h=b8ac64ba&s={SIZE}\" />呼、不知什麼會議的資料總算趕上了&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;<strong>唔？</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://nuwton.com/assets/uploads/2017/06/14987893996x4gj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnuwton.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2F14987893996x4gj.jpg&h=3d663ed5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://nuwton.com/assets/uploads/2017/06/14987898978yh5m.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnuwton.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2F14987898978yh5m.png&h=b91f9674&s={SIZE}\" /><strong>出事啦太姆～～！！出事啦太姆哦～～～！！</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://nuwton.com/assets/uploads/2017/06/149878989252y7g.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnuwton.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2F149878989252y7g.png&h=b8ac64ba&s={SIZE}\" />什..！ 太姆太姆！！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://nuwton.com/assets/uploads/2017/06/14987894017vthx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnuwton.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2F14987894017vthx.jpg&h=e47c84ac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://nuwton.com/assets/uploads/2017/06/149878989252y7g.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnuwton.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2F149878989252y7g.png&h=b8ac64ba&s={SIZE}\" />喂、不是約定好不準來公司的嗎！ 這樣我的<strong>秘密</strong>不就會暴露了嗎！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://nuwton.com/assets/uploads/2017/06/14987898978yh5m.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnuwton.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2F14987898978yh5m.png&h=b91f9674&s={SIZE}\" />因為相當緊急所以沒有辦法太姆！ 在附近的公園、<strong>有壞人出現了</strong>太姆哦！！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://nuwton.com/assets/uploads/2017/06/149878989252y7g.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnuwton.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2F149878989252y7g.png&h=b8ac64ba&s={SIZE}\" />但是、我接下來還有個會議&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://nuwton.com/assets/uploads/2017/06/14987898978yh5m.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnuwton.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2F14987898978yh5m.png&h=b91f9674&s={SIZE}\" />別管了快點『<strong>變身</strong>』吧太姆！！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://nuwton.com/assets/uploads/2017/06/149878989252y7g.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnuwton.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2F149878989252y7g.png&h=b8ac64ba&s={SIZE}\" />不可以！要是在公司變身的話我的秘密不就會暴露了嗎！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://nuwton.com/assets/uploads/2017/06/1498789407hdwgm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnuwton.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2F1498789407hdwgm.jpg&h=fc39a89b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://nuwton.com/assets/uploads/2017/06/14987898978yh5m.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnuwton.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2F14987898978yh5m.png&h=b91f9674&s={SIZE}\" /><strong>得啦快鳩D變身啦太姆～～～！！！！！</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://nuwton.com/assets/uploads/2017/06/1498797961a1lew.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnuwton.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2F1498797961a1lew.jpg&h=77b74799&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://nuwton.com/assets/uploads/2017/06/14987898978yh5m.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnuwton.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2F14987898978yh5m.png&h=b91f9674&s={SIZE}\" /><strong>喂ーーーーーーーーーーーーーーーーーーーーーーーーーーーーーーーーーーーーーーーーーーーーーーーーーーーーーー呀！！！！！！！！！！</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://nuwton.com/assets/uploads/2017/06/149878989252y7g.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnuwton.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2F149878989252y7g.png&h=b8ac64ba&s={SIZE}\" />行了我明白了！！ 真是&hellip;&hellip;沒有你辦法&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://nuwton.com/assets/uploads/2017/06/14987894093ay53.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnuwton.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2F14987894093ay53.gif&h=5172cf94&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">閃亮Dress Up！</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://nuwton.com/assets/uploads/2017/06/14987894128zu38.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnuwton.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2F14987894128zu38.jpg&h=8a6f72da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">魔法少女☆ポプリン！</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n不能對任何人說的&rdquo;秘密&rdquo;&hellip;&hellip;那就是、<strong>在社會上超人氣的魔法少女</strong>、<strong><span style=\"color: violet;\">「魔法少女ポプリン」</span></strong>的真正身份、其實就是我！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://nuwton.com/assets/uploads/2017/06/14987898978yh5m.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnuwton.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2F14987898978yh5m.png&h=b91f9674&s={SIZE}\" />太好了！ 快點去公園把壞人退治吧太姆！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://nuwton.com/assets/uploads/2017/06/14987898959u0wf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnuwton.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2F14987898959u0wf.png&h=4f310cfc&s={SIZE}\" />不、我剛才也說了還有個<strong>會議</strong>要去、先去那邊吧<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://nuwton.com/assets/uploads/2017/06/14987898759whdm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnuwton.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2F14987898759whdm.jpg&h=c3bf4cfd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://nuwton.com/assets/uploads/2017/06/14987982824x61v.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnuwton.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2F14987982824x61v.jpg&h=1507b300&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://nuwton.com/assets/uploads/2017/06/149878987737dcd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnuwton.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2F149878987737dcd.jpg&h=fe8e9e54&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://nuwton.com/assets/uploads/2017/06/14987898978yh5m.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnuwton.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2F14987898978yh5m.png&h=b91f9674&s={SIZE}\" />&hellip;&hellip;還未好嗎太姆？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://nuwton.com/assets/uploads/2017/06/14987898795wst6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnuwton.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2F14987898795wst6.jpg&h=27cd6f79&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://nuwton.com/assets/uploads/2017/06/14987898959u0wf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnuwton.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2F14987898959u0wf.png&h=4f310cfc&s={SIZE}\" />對了、這些資料、對公司外的你要保密<br />\n<img src=\"http://nuwton.com/assets/uploads/2017/06/14987898978yh5m.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnuwton.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2F14987898978yh5m.png&h=b91f9674&s={SIZE}\" />對不起太姆<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>～1小時後～</strong></span></div><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://nuwton.com/assets/uploads/2017/06/149878988177dh3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnuwton.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2F149878988177dh3.jpg&h=d64faa02&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://nuwton.com/assets/uploads/2017/06/14987898959u0wf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnuwton.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2F14987898959u0wf.png&h=4f310cfc&s={SIZE}\" />呼～、把會議的議事錄寫完&hellip;&hellip;好了、終於可以出發了！太姆太姆！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://nuwton.com/assets/uploads/2017/06/14987898978yh5m.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnuwton.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2F14987898978yh5m.png&h=b91f9674&s={SIZE}\" />太好了！ 馬上出發吧太姆～～！！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://nuwton.com/assets/uploads/2017/06/14987898959u0wf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnuwton.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2F14987898959u0wf.png&h=4f310cfc&s={SIZE}\" /><strong>魔法少女、マジかる☆ポプリン出發～～～！！</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://nuwton.com/assets/uploads/2017/06/149878988221hxv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnuwton.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2F149878988221hxv.jpg&h=cc1215e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://nuwton.com/assets/uploads/2017/06/14987898844qjs5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnuwton.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2F14987898844qjs5.jpg&h=7430fdd5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b52a017e38c5e82393e2711a28384091f34cc318","tid":318764,"uid":75969,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T10:21:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://nuwton.com/assets/uploads/2017/06/14987898865il1z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnuwton.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2F14987898865il1z.jpg&h=963baaf8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://nuwton.com/assets/uploads/2017/06/14987898959u0wf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnuwton.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2F14987898959u0wf.png&h=4f310cfc&s={SIZE}\" /><strong>上吧～～～～～～～！！！！</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://nuwton.com/assets/uploads/2017/06/14987898978yh5m.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnuwton.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2F14987898978yh5m.png&h=b91f9674&s={SIZE}\" />社會人士真是辛苦太姆<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>～5分鐘後～</strong></span></div><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://nuwton.com/assets/uploads/2017/06/14987990175419s.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnuwton.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2F14987990175419s.jpg&h=f683af11&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://nuwton.com/assets/uploads/2017/06/14987898978yh5m.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnuwton.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2F14987898978yh5m.png&h=b91f9674&s={SIZE}\" />就是這裡太姆！他就是<strong>壞人</strong>太姆哦！！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://nuwton.com/assets/uploads/2017/06/14987898959u0wf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnuwton.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2F14987898959u0wf.png&h=4f310cfc&s={SIZE}\" />&hellip;&hellip;你！ 你是！！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://nuwton.com/assets/uploads/2017/06/149879901984eml.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnuwton.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2F149879901984eml.jpg&h=a810b780&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://nuwton.com/assets/uploads/2017/06/14987997413dkro.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnuwton.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2F14987997413dkro.png&h=7a3fce5e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://nuwton.com/assets/uploads/2017/06/14987898945f3ue.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnuwton.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2F14987898945f3ue.png&h=ebf7ae54&s={SIZE}\" />哈哈哈、終於來了。這個公園已經由我來佔據了！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://nuwton.com/assets/uploads/2017/06/14987898959u0wf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnuwton.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2F14987898959u0wf.png&h=4f310cfc&s={SIZE}\" />又是你！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://nuwton.com/assets/uploads/2017/06/14987898978yh5m.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnuwton.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2F14987898978yh5m.png&h=b91f9674&s={SIZE}\" />那個傢伙在大學為了尋找和自己一樣的宅朋友、在教室的黑板畫了萌圖被人欺凌的時候也在等著有其他宅來找他、結果沒人把他當成一回事所以從大學退學的凶惡人物太姆～！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://nuwton.com/assets/uploads/2017/06/14987990239yfho.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnuwton.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2F14987990239yfho.jpg&h=47781555&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://nuwton.com/assets/uploads/2017/06/14987898959u0wf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnuwton.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2F14987898959u0wf.png&h=4f310cfc&s={SIZE}\" />公園是屬於大家的遊樂場！ 要是有你這種變態存在的話不就會嚇跑大家嗎！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://nuwton.com/assets/uploads/2017/06/14987898945f3ue.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnuwton.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2F14987898945f3ue.png&h=ebf7ae54&s={SIZE}\" />哼&hellip;&hellip;看來只靠談話是沒有辦法解決！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://nuwton.com/assets/uploads/2017/06/1498798976d74cn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnuwton.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2F1498798976d74cn.jpg&h=d31aefe8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://nuwton.com/assets/uploads/2017/06/14987898978yh5m.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnuwton.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2F14987898978yh5m.png&h=b91f9674&s={SIZE}\" />唔？ 那把杖、總感覺有點奇怪！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://nuwton.com/assets/uploads/2017/06/1498798978ccn2a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnuwton.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2F1498798978ccn2a.jpg&h=873cf569&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://nuwton.com/assets/uploads/2017/06/14987898945f3ue.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnuwton.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2F14987898945f3ue.png&h=ebf7ae54&s={SIZE}\" />哈哈哈！ 這是<strong>藏著劍的手杖</strong>！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://nuwton.com/assets/uploads/2017/06/14987898978yh5m.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnuwton.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2F14987898978yh5m.png&h=b91f9674&s={SIZE}\" />嘿～、果然是很宅的武器！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://nuwton.com/assets/uploads/2017/06/14987898959u0wf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnuwton.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2F14987898959u0wf.png&h=4f310cfc&s={SIZE}\" />&hellip;&hellip;既然是這樣的話只好使出那個了！"},{"pid":"d54b40da7366c0e43e84f463f3f6b6b6e03f951d","tid":318764,"uid":75969,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T10:21:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://nuwton.com/assets/uploads/2017/06/149879898019bgn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnuwton.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2F149879898019bgn.jpg&h=3a2325da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">ポプリン☆Stick！！</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://nuwton.com/assets/uploads/2017/06/1498798982cbh9t.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnuwton.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2F1498798982cbh9t.jpg&h=916929ac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>【ポプリン☆Stick】</strong><br />\n魔法少女マジかるポプリン的武器。前端纏有藏著魔法力量的布、就這樣直接毆打敵人來攻擊。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://nuwton.com/assets/uploads/2017/06/14987898959u0wf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnuwton.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2F14987898959u0wf.png&h=4f310cfc&s={SIZE}\" />要上了太姆太姆！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://nuwton.com/assets/uploads/2017/06/14987898978yh5m.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnuwton.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2F14987898978yh5m.png&h=b91f9674&s={SIZE}\" />來了太姆！！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://nuwton.com/assets/uploads/2017/06/1498798984cim67.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnuwton.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2F1498798984cim67.gif&h=e5fd31e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\"><strong>大家&hellip;&hellip;把力量借給我&hellip;&hellip;</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://nuwton.com/assets/uploads/2017/06/14987989865d94e.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnuwton.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2F14987989865d94e.gif&h=1479cc49&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\"><strong>神聖的魔法哦&hellip;&hellip;將森羅萬象的悲傷轉化為瑪那(MANA)、寄宿在我的身上吧！！<br />\n <br />\n哈～～～～～～！！！</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://nuwton.com/assets/uploads/2017/06/1498798989e5mah.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnuwton.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2F1498798989e5mah.gif&h=a57d764e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\"><strong>ポプリン☆SMASH！！</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://nuwton.com/assets/uploads/2017/06/1498798991eqv1b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnuwton.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2F1498798991eqv1b.jpg&h=51ee88d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://nuwton.com/assets/uploads/2017/06/14987898945f3ue.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnuwton.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2F14987898945f3ue.png&h=ebf7ae54&s={SIZE}\" /><strong>嗚嘩呀呀呀呀！！！！</strong><br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"http://nuwton.com/assets/uploads/2017/06/149879899318p0n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnuwton.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2F149879899318p0n.jpg&h=ee000ac8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://nuwton.com/assets/uploads/2017/06/14987898945f3ue.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnuwton.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2F14987898945f3ue.png&h=ebf7ae54&s={SIZE}\" /><strong>威力比想像中還要強～～～～～～～～！！！！</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://nuwton.com/assets/uploads/2017/06/149879899318p0n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnuwton.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2F149879899318p0n.jpg&h=ee000ac8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://nuwton.com/assets/uploads/2017/06/14987898945f3ue.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnuwton.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2F14987898945f3ue.png&h=ebf7ae54&s={SIZE}\" /><strong>亦因此難受～～～～～～！！！！</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://nuwton.com/assets/uploads/2017/06/14987898978yh5m.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnuwton.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2F14987898978yh5m.png&h=b91f9674&s={SIZE}\" />就是現在！ 給他最後一擊太姆！！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://nuwton.com/assets/uploads/2017/06/14987898959u0wf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnuwton.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2F14987898959u0wf.png&h=4f310cfc&s={SIZE}\" />我知道了！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://nuwton.com/assets/uploads/2017/06/149879899580l0u.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnuwton.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2F149879899580l0u.jpg&h=75cc42da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://nuwton.com/assets/uploads/2017/06/14987898959u0wf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnuwton.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2F14987898959u0wf.png&h=4f310cfc&s={SIZE}\" />這樣就&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://nuwton.com/assets/uploads/2017/06/149879899733e9y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnuwton.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2F149879899733e9y.jpg&h=faf9bd40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://nuwton.com/assets/uploads/2017/06/14987898959u0wf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnuwton.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2F14987898959u0wf.png&h=4f310cfc&s={SIZE}\" />了結了哦～～～～～～！！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://nuwton.com/assets/uploads/2017/06/14987898945f3ue.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnuwton.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2F14987898945f3ue.png&h=ebf7ae54&s={SIZE}\" /><strong>嗚嘩呀呀呀呀！！！</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://nuwton.com/assets/uploads/2017/06/1498798999blwxj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnuwton.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2F1498798999blwxj.jpg&h=5401fe28&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://nuwton.com/assets/uploads/2017/06/14987898945f3ue.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnuwton.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2F14987898945f3ue.png&h=ebf7ae54&s={SIZE}\" /><strong>看到了黑色又蓬鬆的東西～～～！！</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://nuwton.com/assets/uploads/2017/06/1498798999blwxj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnuwton.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2F1498798999blwxj.jpg&h=5401fe28&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://nuwton.com/assets/uploads/2017/06/14987898945f3ue.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnuwton.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2F14987898945f3ue.png&h=ebf7ae54&s={SIZE}\" /><strong>亦因此喪失戰意了～～～～！！！</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://nuwton.com/assets/uploads/2017/06/1498798999blwxj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnuwton.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2F1498798999blwxj.jpg&h=5401fe28&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://nuwton.com/assets/uploads/2017/06/14987898945f3ue.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnuwton.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2F14987898945f3ue.png&h=ebf7ae54&s={SIZE}\" /><strong>所以要回去～～～了</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://nuwton.com/assets/uploads/2017/06/14987898978yh5m.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnuwton.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2F14987898978yh5m.png&h=b91f9674&s={SIZE}\" />太好了！！ 把惡打倒了太姆～～！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://nuwton.com/assets/uploads/2017/06/14987898959u0wf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnuwton.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2F14987898959u0wf.png&h=4f310cfc&s={SIZE}\" />好！ 那就來一下慣例的那個吧！！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://nuwton.com/assets/uploads/2017/06/14988046298wl2e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnuwton.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2F14988046298wl2e.jpg&h=6913e5ed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">ポプリン☆Victory！！</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://nuwton.com/assets/uploads/2017/06/14987990035k3xy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnuwton.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2F14987990035k3xy.jpg&h=1cafd6a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://nuwton.com/assets/uploads/2017/06/14987898959u0wf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnuwton.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2F14987898959u0wf.png&h=4f310cfc&s={SIZE}\" />今天也守護了街道的和平真是太好了！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://nuwton.com/assets/uploads/2017/06/14987898978yh5m.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnuwton.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2F14987898978yh5m.png&h=b91f9674&s={SIZE}\" />都是多得我的建議太姆！ 想再讚賞我多一點呢太姆！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://nuwton.com/assets/uploads/2017/06/14987898959u0wf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnuwton.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2F14987898959u0wf.png&h=4f310cfc&s={SIZE}\" />真是的！ 得意忘形的傢伙！ &hellip;&hellip;&hellip;<span style=\"color: red;\">呀</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://nuwton.com/assets/uploads/2017/06/14987898978yh5m.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnuwton.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2F14987898978yh5m.png&h=b91f9674&s={SIZE}\" />&hellip;&hellip;ポプリン？ 怎麼了太姆？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://nuwton.com/assets/uploads/2017/06/1498799011biqwx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnuwton.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2F1498799011biqwx.jpg&h=782f900f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://nuwton.com/assets/uploads/2017/06/14987990137yenp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnuwton.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2F14987990137yenp.jpg&h=ef9e029e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://nuwton.com/assets/uploads/2017/06/1498799015d2rnj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnuwton.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2F1498799015d2rnj.jpg&h=d9fe7c66&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在這之後、再沒有人看過ポプリン的身影。<br />\n <br />\n但是、一定是在哪裡繼續守護著和平的吧？<br />\n <br />\n一定是這樣、ポプリン&hellip;&